# ferox-audio-sim DDS configuration — both vars optional.
#
# Set both when running cross-machine over a tunnel/VPN/router that drops
# multicast (Tailscale, WireGuard, some venue networks).
#
# Host laptop + Vast.ai compute box over Tailscale:
#   FEROX_DDS_INTERFACE=tailscale0
#   FEROX_DDS_PEERS="100.82.193.45 100.120.68.65"
#
# Host laptop + remote LLM box over Tailscale:
#   FEROX_DDS_INTERFACE=tailscale0
#   FEROX_DDS_PEERS="100.10.10.10"
#
# Host + nav on same LAN (no Tailscale): leave both unset/commented.
